                    Yiğit Alp's programming language license
                             writed at March 1, Friday, 2026
1. usage rights: When my software or the software of the group I am in is misused for malicious purposes, 25% of 
the responsibility is mine and 75% belongs to whoever misused my software. People who use my software for another 
project (2nd party) should add an additional message to tell me that they are using my project.If they violate 
the rights in my software and are honest, and if they will not do it again, I can also accept their apology.

2. non-mandatory:If you detect a bug or security vulnerability in my software, it is not obligatory for you 
to report it to me. You have the right to use my software in the desired and requested way, except for bad 
software and code copying. extra: if you love me, believe that I can feel your hearts = )

3. example code:
yaz: "hi, whats your name?"
değişken name = giriş al:
